Package de.lessvoid.nifty.controls

Class Parameters

java.lang.Object
de.lessvoid.nifty.controls.Parameters
public class Parameters extends Object
All attributes that have been applied to a controlDefinition or the control for that controlDefinition. Please note: some methods in here are duplicates with a different name. This is for easier migration from 1.3.x. I've marked these @Deprecated .
